- Mobile responsive (stack cards vertically on small screens)
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling to match existing dashboard theme

### Update File: dashboard-ui/src/pages/Settings.tsx

Add new "Webhook Configuration" section under existing settings:
- For each strategy, display:
  - Webhook URL (in code block): POST {origin}/api/listener/webhook/{strategy_id}
  - Masked webhook secret: {first-8-chars}...
  - Rotate button that calls POST /strategies/{id}/webhook-secret/rotate
  - Toggle button for webhook_enabled (calls PUT /strategies/{id}/webhook-enabled)
  - Input field for max_daily_signals (calls PUT /strategies/{id}/max-daily-signals)
  - Recent webhook calls list (last 10 calls with status and timestamp)

### Update File: dashboard-ui/src/App.tsx or Navigation Component

